{"tid":1470282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場宣誓大和解","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:44:50.000Z","uid":28358,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ace4cab85b7b4f0f5e512952ecf1828b4494dbf6","tid":1470282,"uid":28358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:45:32.000Z","msg":"我謹此宣誓 本人為有良心香港市民  以光復香港為己任。並承諾不被仇恨支配自己，時刻保持警覺與思考。不搭大台，不割蓆，與抗爭者共進退，光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n若有違此誓 男既俾狗錫春袋 女既錫狗個爛春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3fa1e3d7338136a390f736d51eb12aaaa11092","tid":1470282,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:46:19.000Z","msg":"【重要通知】抗爭不割蓆手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請參閱"},{"pid":"687d815777545c36a1ace9fa999f7b85c8702b7f","tid":1470282,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:46:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74e04c041e3531dde01b28736caebcfa0c60206a","tid":1470282,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:47:11.000Z","msg":"陳雲：<br />\n做錯事不道歉，是違反道德的啊。這個當然，但我們不是在小學課室，由班長和班主任裁判，我們是在戰場上，警察、法官、電視台、報紙、觀眾都是中共的人。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你道歉，對方就有材料展開政治謠言宣傳，而且要求你再為其他你無做過的事道歉（例如毆打北京記者），之後你拒絕，他們就向你開火射擊。</span></span>做錯了事就馬上走，不是道歉！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">普選勝利了，在民選元首認為安全的情況</span></span>，才為以往的錯失道歉，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">道歉也是元首來做，不是民眾來做</span></span>，賠償也是用政府的錢，不是民間眾籌。"},{"pid":"76cfc7ef955f95f37f385f6ece7e03e6b89112d5","tid":1470282,"uid":28358,"like":0,"disli